 (56688005), <a href="/web/20180712202146/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0343386&amp;fLockTerm=Clostridium+difficile+infection">Clostridium difficile infection</a>
 (186431008), <a href="/web/20180712202146/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0040405&amp;fLockTerm=Computerized+axial+tomography">Computerized axial tomography</a>
